You can grab coordinate values from any point in a plot by selecting
[% INCLUDE font/quote a="Cursor" %] from the Plot menu or by typing
[% INCLUDE modkey key="control" letter='.' %].  Text will appear
in the echo area prompting you to click on a point in the plot.  After
you do so, the coordinate values will be displayed in the echo area.

